{"id":"230","name":"this-just-in-antioch-councilwoman-arrested","title":"This Just In: Antioch Councilwoman Arrested","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2008-05-29T12:40:00-05:00","tags":["city council","Nashville","tennessee","vivian wilhoite"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/d29_wilhoite_vivian.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-231\" style=\"border: 0pt none; margin: 3px 8px; float: left;\" title=\"d29_wilhoite_vivian\" src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/d29_wilhoite_vivian.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"123\" height=\"189\"></a>If you live in Metro Council District 29, you may be interested in hearing that your councilwoman <a href=\"http://www.nashville.gov/council/council29.htm\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.nashville.gov&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Vivian Wilhoite</a> was <a href=\"http://www.nashvillecitypaper.com/news.php?viewStory=60515\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.nashvillecitypaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">locked up this morning</a> by Metro police. We wish we could tell you it was something scandalous or even remotely interesting, but it turns out she was just caught driving on a suspended license two weeks ago. She apparently had a few outstanding tickets she failed to pay, which is why her license was suspended, and she paid them the day after she was pulled over. Unfortunately for her, it was too little too late. Though sort of have to chuckle at the thought of a harmless-looking city official in the slammer, we&#x2019;re not sure yet how this affects her seat on the council.</p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}